_99_luftballons.aspx |language= pl}}</ref>\n|23\n|-\n{{singlechart|Sweden|1|artist=Nena|song=99 Luftballons|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 June 2013}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Switzerland|1|artist=Nena|song=99 Luftballons|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 June 2013}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardhot100|2|artist=Nena|artistid=5287|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 June 2013}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US ''Billboard'' [[Dance Club Songs|Dance Club Play]]<ref>{{cite web|title= Nena \u2013 Awards |website= [[AllMusic]] |url= http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nena-mn0000395187/awards |archivedate= 28 May 2016 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20160528051608/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/nena-mn0000395187/awards}}</ref>\n|22\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US ''[[Cashbox (magazine)|Cash Box]]''<ref>{{cite magazine|title= CASH BOX Top 100 Singles \u2013 Week ending MARCH 10, 1984 |magazine= [[Cashbox (magazine)|Cash Box]] |url= http://cashboxmagazine.com/archives/80s_files/19840310.html |archivedate= 30 September 2012 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120930235101/http://cashboxmagazine.com/archives/80s_files/19840310.html}}</ref>\n|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|West Germany|1|artist=Nena|song=99 Luftballons|songid=922|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 June 2013}}\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n====Year-end charts====\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n!Chart (1983)\n!Rank\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Austria ([[\u00d63 Austria Top 40]])<ref>{{cite web|title= Jahreshitparade 1983 |publisher= Austriancharts.at. Hung Medien |accessdate= 17 July 2014 |url= http://www.austriancharts.at/1983_single.asp |language= de}}</ref>\n|17\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Belgium ([[Ultratop|Ultratop 50]] Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|title= Jaaroverzichten 1983 |publisher= [[Ultratop]]. Hung Medien |accessdate= 17 July 2014 |url= http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=1983 |language= nl}}</ref>\n|27\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Germany ([[GfK Entertainment Charts|Official German Charts]])<ref>{{cite web|title= Jahrescharts \u2013 